  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Cambridge Bible for Schools and Colleges",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "35",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". To make it the more solemn and efficacious, the entire installation-ceremony is to be repeated every day for seven days (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 8:33-35",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). In Lev. it is added that the priests are to remain during the whole of the seven days at the entrance of the Tent of Meeting.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
